user-tool: Error, one of the following options is required, --install|--start|--stop|--postprocess

The following options are available:

	--install                 verify this perf tool will work

	--start|stop|postprocess  start/stop/postprocess the data collection
	-d str|--dir=str          directory to store data collection (required)
	--interval=int            number of seconds between each data collection (optional, default is 10 seconds)
	--tool-name=str            you must provide a unique name for this user tool
	--start-script=str         run this user-provided script when starting this tool
	--stop-script=str          run this user-provided script when stopping this tool
	--postproceess-script=str  run this user-provided script when postprocessing this tool
	--file-to-capture=str      capture the contents of this file at each interval
	                           you can use this option, or the start/stop/postprocess-script,
	                           but not both at the same time

	-h|--help                 display this help message
